    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ全国ツアー　北海道にて",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17100,
          "startTime": 17.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ん、朝か……。ふぁ～よく寝た……\nやっぱり寒いな……もう少し布団の中に……",
      "startTime": 11.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、私の布団を引っ張らないでくれる？\n寒いんだけど……",
      "startTime": 22.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6933.3333334,
          "startTime": 29.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ごめん。布団を肩まで掛けて……と、これで良し\n……いや全然良くない！　なぜ瑠依が俺のベッドに！？",
      "startTime": 32.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "る、瑠依！？　どうしてここにいるんだ！？\nはっ！？　ま、ま、まさか俺はとんでもないことを……",
      "startTime": 39.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14199.999999999996,
          "startTime": 53.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "んんっ、{user}さんが夢の中に……？\nふふ、まぁいいわ……むにゃむにゃ……あったか〜い",
      "startTime": 50.333742078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "る、瑠依！？　抱き着くんじゃない！\n起きろ、これは夢じゃなくて、現実だ！！",
      "startTime": 59.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "もぅ……あまり乱暴にしないで下さい……\nそんなに強く揺らされたら、夢から覚めちゃう……",
      "startTime": 67.3097326594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　これ、夢じゃない？　じゃあどうして\n{user}さんがここに？　…………え？",
      "startTime": 78.9430654841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "やっと起きてくれたか、瑠依\n無理やり起こしてすまないんだが、まずは話を……",
      "startTime": 86,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーー！　{user}さん！？\nなんで私のベッドにいるんですか！？",
      "startTime": 92.492860603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ま、ま、まさか……夜中に忍び込んだんですか！？\nい、いいい一体どういうつもりです！？",
      "startTime": 98.7595262524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ご、誤解だ！　ととととりあえず、俺から離れてくれ！\n大体ここは俺の……",
      "startTime": 105.7999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーーー！！　なんで私\n{user}さんに抱き着いてるんですか！？",
      "startTime": 109.4433346108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "優！　危ないからすぐに誰かを呼んで……あれ？\n優が……いない？　え？　私達二人だけ？　えぇ！？",
      "startTime": 115.8100048379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃそうだ、ここは俺の部屋なんだから\n……俺達、一体どうしてこんなことに……！？",
      "startTime": 125.3999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "おお、落ち着いて、ここまでのことを\nおおお、思い出してみましょうか……！",
      "startTime": 131.9411643978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "だ、ダメです、{user}さん\n頭が真っ白で何一つ思い出せません……！",
      "startTime": 137.1744977311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫だ、瑠依。思い出せるところからでいい\n落ち着いて、昨日のことを振り返るんだ",
      "startTime": 144.6999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……それじゃ、私が思い出せるところから\n話しますね",
      "startTime": 153.1168686227,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
