      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ全国ツアー直前",
      "startTime": 155.5168686227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "あら、{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n……書類、凄い量ですね。全国ツアーの準備ですか？",
      "startTime": 162.0502019561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ツアーまでもうすぐだからな。やることが多くて\n……もう次の予約の時間か？　すぐに会議室を空けるよ",
      "startTime": 172.0999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "慌てなくても大丈夫ですよ\n良かったら書類、運ぶの私も手伝います",
      "startTime": 179.3350960092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "助かる。……っと、あれ？\n急に立ち上がったからめまいが……",
      "startTime": 186.2666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
