      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_12_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫ですか！？　だいぶお疲れのようですけど\n食事や睡眠はちゃんと取ってますか？",
      "startTime": 193.5805331544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
